.TH AR7420-hello 7a "June 2012" "plc-utils-2.1.1" "Qualcomm Atheros Powerline Toolkit"
.SH NAME
hello.nvm - simple demonstration applet
.SH SYNOPSIS
.BR plctest  
.BR hello.nvm
.RI [ ... ]
.SH PURPOSE
This applet runs, prints a basic message on the console and returns to the bootloader. It can be used to demonstrate \fBplctest\fR program functionality where one or more applets are to be chained together to form sequence. This applet, together with applet \fBgoodbye.nvm\fR can be ordered and/or merged to illustrate various sequences.
.SH PREREQUISITES
This applet runs on the AR7420 chipset. Bootloader software must be running. SDRAM need not be configured. You must use program \fBplctest\fR to load and execute it.
